Now its time to create the domain object. Lets use create-domain-class target to generate the domain object.
Here is the command which will create Employee.groovy file under the domains directory.
{code}
grails create-domain-class Employee
{code}

Now lets edit the Employee.groovy file to add some attributes to the Employee.
{code}
package emsapp

class Employee {
    String firstName
    String lastName
    Date dob
    String gender
    Boolean active
    Double salary
}
{code}
 